It features a menu with several options, including "Số dư" (Balance), "Công cụ dành cho nhà sáng tạo" (Tools for Creators), "TikTok Studio," "Lịch sử xem" (Watch History), and "Video ngoại tuyến" (Offline Videos). The highlighted section indicates that TikTok Studio is a tool for creators. The top of the screen shows the time and a battery indicator.

flow_desc: The flow begins with the user requesting to fetch their watched video history. First, the user taps the profile icon on the cooking video interface. Next, they navigate to their profile page, which displays engagement metrics and buttons for editing. The user then taps the settings button at the top right corner, leading them to a menu with multiple options. Finally, they select the "Watch History" button to access their previously watched videos, allowing them to view their engagement with past content. This process seamlessly guides the user through their profile to view their video history.
